  "title": "Mellow Earthy Korean Doenjang Pilaf",
  "description": "A diabetic-friendly Korean dish featuring doenjang, with an earthy flavor and flaky texture, inspired by Egyptian cuisine. This pilaf is made with wholesome ingredients and is suitable for a weeknight dinner.",
